title: Sirloin Steak in Tomato Sauce | Gennaro Contaldo
description:
Want to know how to cook perfect steak simmering in juicy, sweet tomato sauce until it's tender and infused with the rich flavour... well, Gennaro Contaldo is here to show you!

He is back with all the love and passions, but in his own home this time. Make sure you let us know in the comments box below what you thought of the dish? Do you have any variations you would put on this? Maybe some red wine? Let us know down below!
